commit.message:
jni.cc (_Jv_JNI_NewObjectArray): Fixed return type.

	* jni.cc (_Jv_JNI_NewObjectArray): Fixed return type.
	* include/jni.h (struct JNINativeInterface) <NewObjectArray>: Now
	returns jobjectArray.
	(_Jv_JNIEnv::NewObjectArray): Likewise.

From-SVN: r90041
